headline: Deals & Moves: Sanctuary Partner Launches $400M RIA; Wealth Enhancement Snags $164M Firm
summary: The summer stays hot for deals and moves, with Carson folding in a partner wealth firm, and Cetera, Osaic and First Manhattan all adding advisors.
